---

## Test Infrastructure Patterns

### Temp Directory Creation
```typescript
function makeTmpDir(): string {
  const dir = path.join(
    os.tmpdir(),
    `ie-test-name-${Date.now()}-${Math.random().toString(36).slice(2)}`,
  );
  mkdirSync(dir, { recursive: true });
  return dir;
}
```

### Cleanup Pattern (Using try/finally)
```typescript
const home = makeTmpDir();
try {
  // Test logic
} finally {
  rmSync(home, { recursive: true, force: true });
}
```

### Mocking Filesystem and System Calls
